data.description: Looking for a spacious desert home with land and views?! Look no further! This lovely 4 bedroom, 2 bath home features 2,356 square feet of living space and is nicely situated on almost 5 ACRES OF LAND with beautiful unobstructed panoramic desert views. Inside you'll be delighted to find a generously sized living space with high ceilings, ceiling fans and large windows that let in an abundance of natural light. The living room flows effortlessly into the kitchen and dining space where you'll find a large island, freshly painted cabinets, ample counter space, an oversized walk-in pantry and a picture window above the sink to take in the gorgeous mountain views. The space just off the kitchen is being used as an office and 5th bonus bedroom (complete with a charming brick-faced fireplace) but can easily be converted back into a second living room, family room or den. Three out of the four bedrooms have large walk in closets and the primary bedroom is complete with an ensuite bathroom featuring a corner soaking tub, separate walk-in shower and 2 individual vanities. There is also a convenient indoor laundry room and dual cooling (AC & Evap Cooling) to keep you comfortable year round. Outside you'll find a detached 2 car garage, beautiful mesquite trees, pens for goats, rabbits and chickens and plenty of space to entertain, expand and store your desert toys!! The roof was replaced April 2021 & the house also has Frontier high speed internet. Located on a quiet street not far from downtown, schools, shopping, eateries, JTNP, and the marine corps base but still far enough away to enjoy all the peace and serenity our desert has to offer. Come take a look & let the desert's allure do the rest, your new desert home or weekend retreat awaits.
